$k_stmts[] = $k_stmt_pre."(11, 161, 'What a whirlwind this year has been!<br />\\r\\nWe were so happy to see everyone at our first concert of the 2017-2017 season this past weekend. We hope you enjoyed it as much as we did. Won&#39;t you join us again this Holiday season?<br />\\r\\nWe will be performing our second concert, entitled Carol of the Angels, on December 6th, 2016 at 7:30 PM. The concert will he held at All Saints Anglican Church, where we will be featuring the music of Vivaldi, Randol Bass, Britten, &amp; Rutter. Help us celebrate the holidays and ring in the New Year.<br />\\r\\n\\r\\n<br /><u>Need to Knows:</u><br />\\r\\n<em>Carol of the Angels</em><br />\\r\\nAll Saints Anglican Church<br />\\r\\nDecember 6th, 2016 at 7:30 PM<br />\\r\\n<strong>Free Admission</strong>\\r\\n', 'What a whirlwind this year has been! We were so happy to see everyone at our first concert of the 2017-2017 season this past weekend. We hope you enjoyed it as much as we did. Won&#039;t you join us again this Holiday season? We will be performing our second concert, entitled Carol of the Angels, on December 6th, 2016 at 7:30 PM. The concert will he held at All Saints Anglican Church, where we will be featuring the music of Vivaldi, Randol Bass, Britten, &amp; Rutter. Help us celebrate the holidays and ring in the New Year. Need to Knows: Carol of the Angels All Saints Anglican Church December 6th, 2016 at 7:30 PM Free Admission');";
